      "role": "user",
      "content": "talking to a counselor won't change the fact that everyone hates me. i see the posts and the comments and it just feels like the whole world decided i'm a bad person. even when i'm home i can't escape it. it's like there's no version of the future where this doesn't follow me. i just feel like i'm trapped in a nightmare that won't end.",
